Package gobblin.eventhub.writer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BatchedEventhubDataWriter
    A batch writer for eventhub, composed by EventhubBatchAccumulator and EventhubDataWriter EventhubBatchAccumulator provides a buffer to store pending records EventhubDataWriter is the actual writer ships data to eventhub
    EventhubBatchAccumulator
    Simply a ttl based batch accumulator for eventhub with string type
    EventhubDataWriter
    Data Writer for Eventhub.
    EventhubDataWriterBuilder
    Builder that hands back a EventhubDataWriter
    EventhubRequest
    The EventhubRequest is a wrapper of given json string This is required because when using eventhub REST api, the json object sent out needs to be wrapped in an outer Body object.
